      "role": "user",
      "content": "well i guess its a bit of both then. but if u had to make a call, isn't it pretty clear that the \"root causes\" approach is more of a long-term solution? like, the \"tough on crime\" stuff feels kind of outdated and focuses more on punishment than actually solving anything, right?",
